
Competition: Copa Mayo
Season: 1910

* Argentina May 29-June 12. All games played in Buenos Aires.


5/29/1910; Uruguay; 3-0; Chile; Colegiales; Jose Susan; 6000
Piendibene 5, Brachi 75, Buck 85;
Uruguay: Saporiti; Bertone, Crocker; Pena, Harley, Zuazú; Buck, Dacal, Piendibene, Raymonda, Brachi
Chile: Gibson; Ashe, McWilliams; Hormazábal, Allen, González; Robson, Simmons, Campbell, Hamilton, Acuña

6/5/1910; Argentina; 5-1; Chile; Gimnasia y Esgrima; Leon Peyrou; 2500
Viale 16, Hayes 26, Hayes 40, Weiss 66, Susan 82; Campbell 50
Argentina: Wilson; Jorge Brown, Juan Brown; Jacobs, E. Brown, Ginocchio; Weiss, Susán, Hayes, Malbrán, Viale
Chile: Gibson; Ashe, McWilliams; Hormazábal, Allen, González; Robson, Campbell, Sturguess, Hamilton, Davidson


6/12/1910; Argentina; 4-1; Uruguay; Gimnasia y Esgrima; Armando Bergalli; 8000
Viale 15, Hayes 43, Watson Hutton 50, Susan 64; Piendibene 58
Argentina: Wilson; Jorge Brown, Juan Brown; Jacobs, E. Brown, Ginocchio; González, Susán, Hayes, Watson Hutton, Viale
Uruguay: Saporiti; Bertone, Benincasa; Pena, Aphesteguy, Zuazú; Buck, Dacal, Piendibene, Raymonda, Brachi



